9;367;7SUBMITdef nejdelsi_slovo(text):\n    a = text.split(" ")\n    z=len(a[0])\n    y=a[0]\n    for i in range(1, len(a)):\n        if len(a[i])>=z:\n            z=len(a[i])\n            y=a[i]\n    return y\n

2;88;1SUBMITdef nejdelsi_slovo(text):\n    slova = text.split(" ")\n    result = ""\n    for slovo in slova:\n        if len(slovo) > len(result) or (len(slovo) == len(result) and slovo < result):\n            result = slovo\n    return result\n

1;33;1SUBMITdef nejdelsi_slovo(text):\n    x = ""\n    for w in text.split():\n        if len(w) > len(x):\n            x = w\n        elif len(w) == len(x):\n            x = min(w,x)\n    return x

2;23;1SUBMITdef nejdelsi_slovo(ret):\n    l=ret.split()\n    l.sort()\n    le=-1\n    for i in l:\n        if len(i)>le:\n            le = len(i)\n    for i in l:\n        if len(i)==le:\n            return i\n
